(40, 14, 4, 11, 21, 19, 19, 'It is not lawful for thee to have her', 'Connection of Law and Judgment', 'This connection highlights the theme of unlawful actions leading to divine judgment. Both passages emphasize the consequences of violating God''s law, as seen in John the Baptist''s condemnation of Herod and Elijah''s pronouncement against Ahab.', 'theme', 0.314, 'high', 'v1.2', 'gpt-4o-mini'),
